precis:
Authority to enter into an AGREEMENT with the Province of Nova Scotia
respecting cost-sharing of the SUMMER EMPLOYMENT EXPERIENCE DEVELOPMENT
(SEED) INITIATIVE, which provides subsidies to employers to encourage them
to hire students during the summer months.
